### Create Order - Invalid Payment Info (Validation Error)
POST {{Microservice.Order.Api_HostAddress}}/v1/orders
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "discount": 0,
  "address": {
    "province": "",
    "city": "",
    "region": "",
    "street": "",
    "postalCode": ""
  },
  "payment": {
    "cardName": "",
    "cardNumber": "1111222233334444",
    "expiration": "13/99",
    "cvv": "12",
    "amount": -100
  },
  "orders": []
}

